"1. Basic Pulse Playback" = "1. 基本脈搏播放";
"- Tap START on the Home screen to open the pulse screen." = "- 在首頁點擊 START 開啟脈搏畫面。";
"- Tap START again to begin black-screen pulse playback." = "- 再次點擊 START，在黑畫面開始脈搏播放。";
"- Double tap the black screen to stop playback." = "- 雙擊黑畫面可停止播放。";
"- Double tap when leaving pulse measurement playback." = "- 離開脈搏測量播放時也請雙擊。";
"2. Pulse Controls" = "2. 脈搏控制";
"- Pulse slider: sets regular pulse rate in bpm." = "- 脈搏滑桿：設定規則心率（bpm）。";
"- Pulse (Weak): lowers haptic intensity to simulate weaker palpation." = "- 脈搏（微弱）：降低觸覺強度以模擬較弱觸診。";
"3. Arrhythmia Modes" = "3. 心律不整模式";
"- Arrhythmia (PVC): simulates premature beats with compensatory pause." = "- 心律不整（PVC）：模擬早期收縮與代償性停頓。";
"- Arrhythmia (AF): simulates irregularly irregular rhythm." = "- 心律不整（AF）：模擬完全不規則節律。";
"- Only one arrhythmia mode can be ON at a time." = "- 同一時間只能開啟一種心律不整模式。";
"4. AF Sliders (Settings Sheet)" = "4. AF 滑桿（設定面板）";
"- Mean Rate (bpm): average ventricular rate target during AF." = "- 平均心率（bpm）：AF 時平均心室率目標。";
"- Irregularity (%): variability of beat-to-beat interval." = "- 不規則度（%）：相鄰心搏間期變化程度。";
"  - Lower value: rhythm feels closer to regular." = "  - 數值越低：節律越接近規則。";
"  - Higher value: rhythm feels more chaotic." = "  - 數值越高：節律越混亂。";
"5. Set Data Workflow" = "5. 資料集流程";
"- Open Set Data from Home bottom navigation." = "- 在首頁底部導覽開啟 Set Data。";
"- Tap + to build a new SET profile." = "- 點擊 + 建立新的 SET 設定檔。";
"- Tap SET to save." = "- 點擊 SET 儲存。";
"- Tap a row to play that saved pattern on black screen." = "- 點擊列表列可在黑畫面播放已儲存模式。";
"- Swipe left on a row to delete it." = "- 向左滑動列表列可刪除。";
